                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The statistic of the inelastic and transfer",
                "peaks was poor, but good enough for the following",
                "analysis. The estimated overall uncertainty of the",
                "inelastic and transfer cross sections ranges",
                "from 12 to 35%."
              ]
            }
